## Non-Functional Requirements

### Performance
- First Contentful Paint: < 1.5s on 4G
- Time to Interactive: < 3s
- API response time: < 200ms for reads, < 500ms for writes
- All async operations must show loading state within 100ms

### Security
{% if tech_profile.needs_auth %}
- All authenticated routes require valid JWT
- Implement CSRF protection on all mutation endpoints
- Store secrets in environment variables, never in code
- Enable RLS on all Supabase tables
{% endif %}
- Sanitise all user input (XSS prevention)
- Rate limit API endpoints (100 req/min per IP)
- HTTPS only in production

### Accessibility
- WCAG 2.1 AA compliance minimum
- All images have descriptive alt text
- Form inputs have associated labels
- Colour contrast ratio ≥ 4.5:1 for all text
- Keyboard navigation for all interactive elements
- Screen reader compatible (ARIA labels on icons)

### Reliability
- Handle network failures gracefully with retry UI
- Optimistic updates for instant perceived performance
- Offline detection with user-friendly message
{% if tech_profile.scale_tier != "prototype" %}

### Scalability ({{ tech_profile.scale_tier }})
- Target: {{ tech_profile.estimated_users_month1 }} users month 1
- Database connection pooling enabled
- Implement pagination for all list endpoints (max 50 items)
{% endif %}
